item.title: singing some gracie abrams by the lake
item.description:
hii welcome back!! I spent of few days up at my family's cottage in Lac Saint-Jean and figured I'd sing a little something by the lake for ya. I think that most of my song requests at this point are ones by Gracie so I hope you guys enjoy this one! Also in case you missed it, I announced a small European tour next November supporting Bertie Newman, and couldn't be more excited to perform for the first time in Europe :) tickets are available with the link below and you can follow my Instagram for more updates! Thanks for being here and for listening, take care everyone xxx
https://linktr.ee/mariannebeaulieu

#cover #gracie #calm #acoustic
